OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with long clear periods.
OL,7,FPatches of cloud are likely to drift
OL,8,Facross from the north overnight,
OL,9,Fthough it should stay dry. Some patchy
OL,10,Fmist or fog potentially developing
OL,11,Facross Devon and Cornwall. Quite warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FAnother largely fine day is
OL,14,Fexpected on Saturday with some warm
OL,15,Fsunshine developing. However, cloud
OL,16,Fwill increase from the northwest later
OL,17,Fon in the day, bringing some patchy
OL,18,Flight rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
