OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fwill be a fresher, still breezy day
OL,7,Fwith sunshine and a few light showers.
OL,8,FMostly dry early on next week, with
OL,9,Fsome sunny spells, especially in the
OL,10,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
